T1  - Computational Algorithm for the Sequential Unconstrained Minimization Technique for Nonlinear Programming
AU  - Fiacco, Anthony V.
AU  - McCormick, Garth P.
Y1  - 1964/07/01
PY  - 1964
DA  - 1964/07/01
